# Encryption Decryption Tool

## Project Description
This is a simple encryption and decryption tool created using C programming.

The program converts plain text into encrypted text and decrypts it back to the original message.

## Features
- Encrypt text
- Decrypt text
- Simple command line interface

## Technologies Used
- C Programming
- String manipulation
- Basic cryptography logic

## How to Run

1. Compile the program
gcc encryption.c

2. Run the program
./a.out

3. Enter message to encrypt or decrypt

## Example

Input:
hello

Encrypted:
khoor

Decrypted:
hello

